                        <cell><p><m>\hphantom{0000}</m> </p></cell>
                        <cell><p><m>\hphantom{0000}</m> </p></cell>
                    </row>
            </tabular></table>
            <ol labels="*a*">
                <li><p>Write an equation that expresses the amount of gas, <m>g</m>, in Leon's fuel tank in terms of the number of miles, <m>m</m>, he has driven.</p></li>
                <li><p>Graph the equation.
                    <image source="images/fig-ex-1-1-4" alt="grid" width="50%"/> </p></li>
