                <li><p>Write an equation for the annual driving cost, <m>C</m>, in terms of <m>d</m>, the number of miles driven.</p></li>
                <li><p>Complete the table of values.
                    <table><tabular top="major" halign="center" right="minor" left="minor" bottom="minor">
                        <col halign="left"/>
                            <row bottom="minor">
                                <cell><p>Miles Driven</p></cell>
                                <cell><p><m>4000</m></p></cell>
                                <cell><p><m>8000</m></p></cell>
